( Carnage: Yes, but Carnage does not know that.)

** Carnage breathed heard as she watched the shots go over Instrat's head, 
growling and readying her weapon to fire again.
But then she suddenly heard Instrat say something about honor, something 
that made her cringe as well as remember how Dinobot always use to rant 
about it.
Honor?
Her?
Get real!!
She had murdered bots in their sleep in her past, and there was no honor in 
that.
Nor in attacking a bot 2 against 1. It was uneven odds...but Carnage had not 
payed attention to honor no matter how much people told her about it...and 
how many times Dinobot tried to pound it into her skull.
Carnage didn't lower her rifle as Instrat lowered her weapons. Making sure 
to keep a close watch on her.

Beside her, Teltili looked un confusion as Instrat spoke and lowered her 
scythe.
What was up with thi?
Only seconds ago this woman was trying to chop their heads off!
Teltili glanced towards Carnage for a moment and saw that she kept her 
weapin upraised, then moving to keep her dart gun aimed towards the enemy.

Carnage growled for a moment, keeping her weapon aimed towards Instrat's 
head.**

" Honorable?"
